oundaries: The Nation, the States, the Rectangular Survey|first=Bill|last=Hubbard, Jr.|year=2009|url=https://books.google.com/?id=LMacwod5KLwC&pg=PA140|publisher=[[University of Chicago Press]]|location=Chicago|isbn=978-0-226-35591-7|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Joseph|first=John Earl|title=Language and Politics|publisher=[[Edinburgh University Press]]|location=Edinburgh|year=2006|isbn=978-0-7486-2453-9|url=https://books.google.com/?id=pJu5veUAo7kC&pg=PA63|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=McGraw|first=Eliza|title=Two Covenants: Representations of Southern Jewishness|publisher=[[Louisiana State University Press]]|location=Baton Rouge|date=June 24, 2005|isbn=978-0-8071-3043-8|url=https://books.google.com/?id=EzR13rJBwc4C&pg=PA14|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last1=Miller|first1=Kerby A.|first2=Arnold|last2=Schrier|first3=Bruce D.|last3=Boling|first4=David N.|last4=Doyle|title=Irish immigrants in the land of Canaan|url=https://books.google.com/?id=bq79_YZ8ViIC|publisher=[[Oxford University Press]]|year=2003|isbn=978-0-19-504513-0|location=New York|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Moran|first=Michael G.|title=Inventing Virginia: Sir Walter Raleigh and the Rhetoric of Colonization, 1584\u20131590|publisher=[[Peter Lang (publishing company)|Peter Lang]]|location=New York|year=2007|isbn=978-0-8204-8694-9|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Morgan|first=Lynda|title=Emancipation in Virginia's Tobacco Belt, 1850\u20131870|publisher=[[University of Georgia Press]]|location=Athens, GA|year=1992|isbn=978-0-8203-1415-0|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Morgan|first=Philip D.|title=Slave Counterpoint|location=Chapel Hill|publisher=[[University of North Carolina Press]]|year=1998|isbn=978-0-8078-4717-6|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Palmer|first=Tim|title=America by Rivers|publisher=[[Island Press]]|year=1998|location=Washington, D.C.|isbn=978-1-55963-264-5|url=https://books.google.com/?id=ctA1eNFvI-oC&pg=PA49|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite book|last=Pazzaglia|first=Frank James|title=Excursions in Geology